{"id":2574,"date":"2021-11-18T11:50:52","date_gmt":"2021-11-18T19:50:52","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/?page_id=2574"},"modified":"2023-01-17T09:11:11","modified_gmt":"2023-01-17T16:11:11","slug":"history","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/about\/history\/","title":{"rendered":"History"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<div class=\"wp-block-cover has-background-dim is-style-hero-inside\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1707\" class=\"wp-block-cover__image-background wp-image-2107\" alt=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/LEM-MYR-Group-family-is-born-Nansemond-River-Project-012-3-scaled.jpg\" style=\"object-position:55% 50%\" data-object-fit=\"cover\" data-object-position=\"55% 50%\" srcset=\"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/LEM-MYR-Group-family-is-born-Nansemond-River-Project-012-3-scaled.jpg 2560w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/LEM-MYR-Group-family-is-born-Nansemond-River-Project-012-3-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/LEM-MYR-Group-family-is-born-Nansemond-River-Project-012-3-1600x1067.jpg 1600w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/LEM-MYR-Group-family-is-born-Nansemond-River-Project-012-3-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/LEM-MYR-Group-family-is-born-Nansemond-River-Project-012-3-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/LEM-MYR-Group-family-is-born-Nansemond-River-Project-012-3-2048x1365.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" \/><div class=\"wp-block-cover__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-cover-is-layout-flow\">\n<h1 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A History to be proud of<\/h1>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-layout-flex wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link\" href=\"#learn-more\"><meta charset=\"utf-8\">Learn More <img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-316\" style=\"width: NaNpx;\" src=\"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/arrow-down.svg\" alt=\"\"><\/a><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div id=\"learn-more\" class=\"wp-block-group is-style-block-section has-myrgroup-gray-very-light-background-color has-background\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns timeline-wrapper is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-1 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" id=\"history\">\n<h2 class=\"has-black-color has-text-color wp-block-heading\"><sup>Our History<\/sup>Over a Century of <span class=\"has-inline-color has-myrgroup-blue-color\">Success<\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-myrgroup-history-timeline\">\r\n\r\n    <div class=\"timeline-item\">\r\n\r\n    <img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"524\" height=\"630\" src=\"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/InTheLate1800sLEMyersHistory_MyersEdison.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large\" alt=\"Lewis Edward Myers and Thomas Edison in a factory\" \/>    <h3 class=\"has-black-color has-text-color\">In the late 1800s \u2013 Bringing Electricity to American Homes<\/h3>\r\n    <p>MYR Group\u2019s oldest subsidiary, The L.E. Myers Co. (L.E. Myers) was established in 1891. The company\u2019s founder, Lewis Edward Myers, was a salesman for the American inventor Thomas Edison, who dreamed of making the new, modern convenience of electricity available and affordable to American homes and businesses. Myers founded L.E. Myers in Chicago, Illinois, where he landed his first street lighting job and went on to building the foundation for a long and successful business venture in electrical construction.<\/p>\n\r\n  <\/div>\r\n    <div class=\"timeline-item\">\r\n\r\n    <img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1048\" height=\"689\" src=\"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/InThe1900LEMOptionChicagoDowntown.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large\" alt=\"Industrialization of America\" srcset=\"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/InThe1900LEMOptionChicagoDowntown.jpg 1048w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/InThe1900LEMOptionChicagoDowntown-1024x673.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/InThe1900LEMOptionChicagoDowntown-768x505.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1048px) 100vw, 1048px\" \/>    <h3 class=\"has-black-color has-text-color\">In the 1900s \u2013 The Industrialization of America<\/h3>\r\n    <p class=\"p1\">Throughout the early 1900\u2019s, L.E. Myers played an instrumental role in building the nation\u2019s electrical infrastructure \u2013 a crucial development to the industrialization of America. The company established a strong presence and industry reputation, especially throughout the Midwest.<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n\r\n  <\/div>\r\n    <div class=\"timeline-item\">\r\n\r\n    <img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1028\" src=\"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Christmas-lights-City-and-County-Building-2-3-1600x1028.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large\" alt=\"Christmas lights on the city and county building\" srcset=\"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Christmas-lights-City-and-County-Building-2-3-1600x1028.jpg 1600w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Christmas-lights-City-and-County-Building-2-3-1024x658.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Christmas-lights-City-and-County-Building-2-3-768x494.jpg 768w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Christmas-lights-City-and-County-Building-2-3-1536x987.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Christmas-lights-City-and-County-Building-2-3-2048x1316.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" \/>    <h3 class=\"has-black-color has-text-color\">Early 1900s \u2013 The Invention of Christmas Lights<\/h3>\r\n    <p class=\"p1\">In 1912, Sturgeon Electric Company, Inc. (Sturgeon Electric) was founded by David Dwight \u201cD.D.\u201d Sturgeon in Denver, Colorado. Legend tells that D.D. Sturgeon invented colored Christmas lights in 1914. To cheer his ailing son, Sturgeon dipped ordinary lightbulbs in paint, strung them on a cord, and hung them on a tree outside his home near his son\u2019s bedroom window. Word spread quickly, and folks came from miles away to view the lights outside the Sturgeons\u2019 home. Today, the company donates time and services for various outdoor lighting displays throughout Denver.<\/p>\n\r\n  <\/div>\r\n    <div class=\"timeline-item\">\r\n\r\n    <img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1092\" src=\"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/ESBoulos-1600x1092.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large\" alt=\"Group of workers in front of a E.S. Boulos Co. truck\" srcset=\"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/ESBoulos-1600x1092.jpg 1600w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/ESBoulos-1024x699.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/ESBoulos-768x524.jpg 768w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/ESBoulos-1536x1048.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/ESBoulos-2048x1398.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" \/>    <h3 class=\"has-black-color has-text-color\">In the 1920s \u2013 A Boy with a Plan<\/h3>\r\n    <p class=\"p1\">Edward S. Boulos was only 13 when he launched his electrical career in Portland, Maine. After founding the E.S. Boulos Company (E.S. Boulos) in 1920, the company expanded quickly, and by 1947, Boulos operated an expansive warehouse and elegant showroom where the company displayed a full line of radios, light fixtures, and household appliances.<\/p>\n\r\n  <\/div>\r\n    <div class=\"timeline-item\">\r\n\r\n    <img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"888\" height=\"614\" src=\"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/InThe1940sLEMMilitary.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large\" alt=\"Man working on the cockpit of a military plane\" srcset=\"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/InThe1940sLEMMilitary.jpg 888w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/InThe1940sLEMMilitary-768x531.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 888px) 100vw, 888px\" \/>    <h3 class=\"has-black-color has-text-color\">In the 1940s \u2013 Powering Military Industries <\/h3>\r\n    <p class=\"p1\">In 1940, C. Allen Harlan founded Harlan Electric Company (Harlan Electric) in Detroit, Michigan. In its infancy, Harlan Electric quickly earned an enviable reputation for quality construction and value engineering. When the 1941 attack on Pearl Harbor thrust the country into World War II, the build-up of military capabilities began in earnest. Harlan Electric was awarded a contract with the American Propeller Corporation to perform the electrical scope for a new facility to support the wartime effort.<\/p>\n\r\n  <\/div>\r\n    <div class=\"timeline-item\">\r\n\r\n    <img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1557\" height=\"1095\" src=\"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/InThe1950sLEMT-Line.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large\" alt=\"Group of workers assembling the wires of a transmission tower\" srcset=\"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/InThe1950sLEMT-Line.jpg 1557w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/InThe1950sLEMT-Line-1024x720.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/InThe1950sLEMT-Line-768x540.jpg 768w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/InThe1950sLEMT-Line-1536x1080.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1557px) 100vw, 1557px\" \/>    <h3 class=\"has-black-color has-text-color\">In the 1950s \u2013 Tapping into Transmission Line Construction<\/h3>\r\n    <p class=\"p1\">In 1953, L.E. Myers built the nation\u2019s first 345kV transmission lines for the Ohio Valley Electric Corporation. As the decades progress, the company pioneers the use of helicopters for hauling and installing transmission towers.<\/p>\n\r\n  <\/div>\r\n    <div class=\"timeline-item\">\r\n\r\n    <img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"603\" height=\"682\" src=\"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Early1970sWPEPhoto.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large\" alt=\"Dieter fettback and ernie moore enjoying a bottle of alcohol\" \/>    <h3 class=\"has-black-color has-text-color\">Early 1970s \u2013 Moving Business North<\/h3>\r\n    <p class=\"p1\">Western Pacific Enterprises, Ltd. (WPE), MYR Group\u2019s Canadian subsidiary, began in 1973 in Coquitlam, British Columbia. Founders Dieter Fettback and Ernie Moore mortgaged their homes to start an electrical contracting company that has grown to one of the largest contracting firms in western Canada thanks to its founders\u2019 unwavering vision to deliver efficient and safe commercial, civil, and industrial assignments.<\/p>\n\r\n  <\/div>\r\n    <div class=\"timeline-item\">\r\n\r\n    <img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1190\" height=\"1585\" src=\"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/InThe1980sHuenNavyPierOPTION1.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large\" alt=\"Birdseye view of the chicago children&#039;s museum\" srcset=\"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/InThe1980sHuenNavyPierOPTION1.jpg 1190w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/InThe1980sHuenNavyPierOPTION1-769x1024.jpg 769w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/InThe1980sHuenNavyPierOPTION1-768x1023.jpg 768w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/InThe1980sHuenNavyPierOPTION1-1153x1536.jpg 1153w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1190px) 100vw, 1190px\" \/>    <h3 class=\"has-black-color has-text-color\">Mid-to-late 1970s \u2013 Boosting Capabilities in Substation Construction<\/h3>\r\n    <p class=\"p1\">In 1977, Great Southwestern Construction Inc. (Great Southwestern) opened its doors as a family-owned business founded by Bob Martinez in Castle Rock, Colorado. Great Southwestern earned its reputation as a trusted contractor by specializing in power delivery projects throughout the desert Southwest and Rocky Mountain region. By the mid-1980s, the company was awarded a substantial contract for work associated with the Central Arizona Irrigation Project, paving the way for rapid growth, especially in substation construction.<\/p>\n\r\n  <\/div>\r\n    <div class=\"timeline-item\">\r\n\r\n    <img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1200\" height=\"1600\" src=\"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/InThe1980sHuenHughes-McGovernOPTION2-1200x1600.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large\" alt=\"Mike hughes and jim mcgovern reviewing a blueprint\" srcset=\"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/InThe1980sHuenHughes-McGovernOPTION2-1200x1600.jpg 1200w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/InThe1980sHuenHughes-McGovernOPTION2-768x1024.jpg 768w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/InThe1980sHuenHughes-McGovernOPTION2-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/InThe1980sHuenHughes-McGovernOPTION2-1536x2048.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/InThe1980sHuenHughes-McGovernOPTION2-scaled.jpg 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" \/>    <h3 class=\"has-black-color has-text-color\">In the 1980s \u2013 Starting Small<\/h3>\r\n    <p class=\"p1\">Huen Electric\u2019s humble beginnings date to 1983, when founders Mike Hughes and Jim McGovern launched the company in Chicago with nothing more than a rusty pickup truck, a small cache of tools, and a tiny office filled with a card table and chairs. By the early 1990\u2019s Huen Electric was performing electrical installations at many Chicago landmarks, including Wrigley Field, the Sears Tower, and the Navy Pier.<\/p>\n\r\n  <\/div>\r\n    <div class=\"timeline-item\">\r\n\r\n    <img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1065\" src=\"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Prologis-Solar-w-Workers-1600x1065.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large\" alt=\"Two workers talking in a field of solar panels\" srcset=\"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Prologis-Solar-w-Workers-1600x1065.jpg 1600w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Prologis-Solar-w-Workers-1024x681.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Prologis-Solar-w-Workers-768x511.jpg 768w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Prologis-Solar-w-Workers-1536x1022.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Prologis-Solar-w-Workers-2048x1363.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" \/>    <h3 class=\"has-black-color has-text-color\">Early 1990s \u2013 Premier Provider of Energy in California <\/h3>\r\n    <p class=\"p1\">CSI Electrical Contractors, Inc. was founded by Steve Watts and opened for business in 1990 in Santa Fe Springs, Calif. Since then, the company has emerged as a full-service leader in highly technical and innovative electrical design and construction, with a reputation as a premier provider of renewable energy development, installation, and maintenance.<\/p>\n\r\n  <\/div>\r\n    <div class=\"timeline-item\">\r\n\r\n    <img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1067\" src=\"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/LEM-MYR-Group-family-is-born-Nansemond-River-Project-012-3-1600x1067.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large\" alt=\"Two transmission towers during a sunset\" srcset=\"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/LEM-MYR-Group-family-is-born-Nansemond-River-Project-012-3-1600x1067.jpg 1600w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/LEM-MYR-Group-family-is-born-Nansemond-River-Project-012-3-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/LEM-MYR-Group-family-is-born-Nansemond-River-Project-012-3-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/LEM-MYR-Group-family-is-born-Nansemond-River-Project-012-3-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/LEM-MYR-Group-family-is-born-Nansemond-River-Project-012-3-2048x1365.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" \/>    <h3 class=\"has-black-color has-text-color\">Mid 1990s \u2013 The MYR Group Family is Born<\/h3>\r\n    <p class=\"p1\">By the 1990\u2019s, L.E. Myers\u2019 desire to expand operationally and geographically culminated with the acquisitions of Sturgeon Electric and Harlan Electric. In 1995, MYR Group Inc. (MYR Group) was established as the holding company of L.E. Myers, Sturgeon Electric, and Harlan Electric and grew to one of the largest holding companies of specialty electrical contractors in the U.S. and Canada.<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n\r\n  <\/div>\r\n    <div class=\"timeline-item\">\r\n\r\n    <img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1600\" height=\"680\" src=\"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/InThe2000sMYRPublicNASDAQ-scaled-e1635277957499-1600x680.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large\" alt=\"Digital billboard of the MYR Group logo\" srcset=\"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/InThe2000sMYRPublicNASDAQ-scaled-e1635277957499-1600x680.jpg 1600w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/InThe2000sMYRPublicNASDAQ-scaled-e1635277957499-1024x435.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/InThe2000sMYRPublicNASDAQ-scaled-e1635277957499-768x326.jpg 768w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/InThe2000sMYRPublicNASDAQ-scaled-e1635277957499-1536x653.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/InThe2000sMYRPublicNASDAQ-scaled-e1635277957499-2048x870.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" \/>    <h3 class=\"has-black-color has-text-color\">In the 2000s \u2013 MYR Group Goes Public<\/h3>\r\n    <p class=\"p1\">MYR Group went public in 2008, trading on the NASDAQ under the symbol MYRG. As growth is a key part of MYR Group\u2019s strategy, the company acquired Great Southwestern Construction, Inc. in 2000, E.S. Boulos Company and High Country Line Construction in 2015, Western Pacific Enterprises Ltd. in 2016, Huen Electric in 2018, and CSI Electrical Contractors in 2019.<\/p>\n\r\n  <\/div>\r\n    <div class=\"timeline-item\">\r\n\r\n    <img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1600\" height=\"899\" src=\"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/InThe2000sLargerComplexProjLEM-MPRP-1600x899.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large\" alt=\"Worker crouched on the beam of a transmission tower\" srcset=\"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/InThe2000sLargerComplexProjLEM-MPRP-1600x899.jpg 1600w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/InThe2000sLargerComplexProjLEM-MPRP-1024x575.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/InThe2000sLargerComplexProjLEM-MPRP-768x432.jpg 768w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/InThe2000sLargerComplexProjLEM-MPRP-1536x863.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/InThe2000sLargerComplexProjLEM-MPRP-2048x1151.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" \/>    <h3 class=\"has-black-color has-text-color\">In the 2000s \u2013 Larger and More Complex Projects<\/h3>\r\n    <p class=\"p1\">A major transmission build-out and modernization effort was under way in the U.S. with much of our nation\u2019s infrastructure built in the 1940s and 1950s. MYR Group subsidiaries completed several significant projects during this time \u2013 most notably, at the time, the $232 million \u201cNorthern Loop\u201d of the Maine Power Reliability Program (MPRP), the largest energy infrastructure project in state history.<\/p>\n\r\n  <\/div>\r\n    <div class=\"timeline-item\">\r\n\r\n    <img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1600\" height=\"899\" src=\"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/In2009-MYREBattleMtn-1600x899.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large\" alt=\"Group of workers inserting solar panels\" srcset=\"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/In2009-MYREBattleMtn-1600x899.jpg 1600w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/In2009-MYREBattleMtn-1024x575.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/In2009-MYREBattleMtn-768x432.jpg 768w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/In2009-MYREBattleMtn-1536x863.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/In2009-MYREBattleMtn-2048x1151.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" \/>    <h3 class=\"has-black-color has-text-color\">In 2009 \u2013 Completing Complex &amp; Renewable Transmission Projects<\/h3>\r\n    <p class=\"p1\">In 2009, MYR Transmission Services, Inc. (MYRT) was established to better meet the needs of clients constructing large and complex transmission projects. As the interest for a more sustainable future led by clean energy increased, the company rebranded to MYR Energy Services, Inc., providing specialized engineer-procure-construct (EPC) services on large transmission and substation construction projects and renewable energy project delivery, including utility-scale solar and energy storage installations.<\/p>\n\r\n  <\/div>\r\n    <div class=\"timeline-item\">\r\n\r\n    <img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1600\" src=\"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/EPC-HCLC-Sloan-Canyon-3-1600x1600.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large\" alt=\"Group of workers smiling at a construction site\" srcset=\"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/EPC-HCLC-Sloan-Canyon-3-1600x1600.jpg 1600w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/EPC-HCLC-Sloan-Canyon-3-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/EPC-HCLC-Sloan-Canyon-3-782x782.jpg 782w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/EPC-HCLC-Sloan-Canyon-3-768x768.jpg 768w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/EPC-HCLC-Sloan-Canyon-3-1536x1536.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/EPC-HCLC-Sloan-Canyon-3-2048x2048.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" \/>    <h3 class=\"has-black-color has-text-color\">In the 2010s \u2013 A Strong Player in the World of EPC<\/h3>\r\n    <p class=\"p1\">In 2013, MYR Group\u2019s youngest subsidiary at the time &#8211; High Country Line Construction, Inc. (HCLC) &#8211; opened its doors in Morgan, Utah. Founder Clay Thomson grew the company from the ground-up by providing a full-range of capabilities related to transmission, distribution, and substation construction. Now a forceful player on EPC projects throughout the western United States, HCLC frequently partners with MYR Group subsidiaries on projects throughout the nation.<\/p>\n\r\n  <\/div>\r\n    <div class=\"timeline-item\">\r\n\r\n    <img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1600\" src=\"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/US-Canada-BLANK-MAP-1600x1600.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large\" alt=\"Collage of MYR Group staff on the map of Canada and USA\" srcset=\"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/US-Canada-BLANK-MAP-1600x1600.jpg 1600w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/US-Canada-BLANK-MAP-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/US-Canada-BLANK-MAP-782x782.jpg 782w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/US-Canada-BLANK-MAP-768x768.jpg 768w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/US-Canada-BLANK-MAP-1536x1536.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/US-Canada-BLANK-MAP-2048x2048.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" \/>    <h3 class=\"has-black-color has-text-color\">Today \u2013 A Proud Network of Companies<\/h3>\r\n    <p class=\"p1\">MYR Group subsidiaries have the experience and expertise to complete electrical installations of any type and size, providing services within two segments \u2013 Transmission &amp; Distribution (T&amp;D) and Commercial &amp; Industrial (C&amp;I). With thousands of skilled employees, extensive fleet resources, and strong financial positioning, we serve the utility, commercial business, renewable energy, and municipality markets throughout the United States and Canada.<\/p>\n\r\n  <\/div>\r\n    <div class=\"timeline-item\">\r\n\r\n    <img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1600\" src=\"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Future-WELLS-SOLAR-FIELD-000-3-1600x1600.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large\" alt=\"Worker carrying and inserting a solar panel\" srcset=\"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Future-WELLS-SOLAR-FIELD-000-3-1600x1600.jpg 1600w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Future-WELLS-SOLAR-FIELD-000-3-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Future-WELLS-SOLAR-FIELD-000-3-782x782.jpg 782w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Future-WELLS-SOLAR-FIELD-000-3-768x768.jpg 768w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Future-WELLS-SOLAR-FIELD-000-3-1536x1536.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Future-WELLS-SOLAR-FIELD-000-3-2048x2048.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" \/>    <h3 class=\"has-black-color has-text-color\">Future \u2013 Well-Positioned for Continued Growth &amp; Success<\/h3>\r\n    <p class=\"p1\">MYR Group has achieved more than a century of success by embracing smart technologies, strengthening our execution strategies, and investing in our people by continually expanding our training programs and building a culture of inclusion. As we continue to provide critical electrical infrastructure services that help power a clean energy future, our top priorities are unwavering: reduce our environmental impact, protect the wellbeing of our people, and support the communities where we live and work.<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n\r\n  <\/div>\r\n  \r\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column timeline-image-wrapper is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-style-block-section footer-call-to-action\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns has-myrgroup-blue-background-color has-background is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-2 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:66.66%\">\n<h2 class=\"has-white-color has-text-color wp-block-heading\">Strength in Our legacy and success are directly attributed to our network of companies<\/h2>\n\n\n\n\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:33.33%\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-layout-flex wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link\" href=\"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/subsidiaries\/\">LEARN MORE<\/a><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n","protecte